⁦🎙️⁩ Ferran Torres: &quot;I am so happy to be joining Manchester City. Every player wants to be involved in attacking teams and they're one of the most attacking in world football. Pep encourages a really open, aggressive style, which I love..&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;He is a manager with a proven track record of improving players. To have him overseeing my development is a dream. The Club have won plenty of trophies in the last 10 years and I hope I can play a role in continuing that success..&quot;

⁦🎙️⁩ Ferran Torres: &quot;My agent was in Manchester with the club, he called and said they reached an agreement and that I would play for Manchester City. It is a club that aims to win everything and has the best coach in the world. I will improve and learn many things there..&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;It was a very emotional time for me. Pep Guardiola passed on a lot of tranquility to me and congratulated me. That helped me calm down a lot..&quot;

Eric Garcia REJECTS new City contract!<br />
<br />
Pep Guardiola on Eric Garcia rejecting a contract at Manchester City: &quot;He said he does not want to extend but we wanted him to, so he will play at another place&quot;
